Senior Construction Associate 5-8PQE, Abu Dhabi
Senior Construction Associate 5-8PQE, Abu Dhabi
Location:  --Abu Dhabi
This well established US law firm is currently recruiting for a senior construction associate to join the highly regarded team in Abu Dhabi.
The ideal candidate will be 5+ PQE (up to Counsel level) and have solid construction experience from a highly regarded US or international law firm. GCC experience is preferred, but not essential – strong lawyers from the UK, Australia or New Zealand will also be considered.
The team has particular skills in construction, operation and maintenance of major energy and infrastructure projects throughout the Middle East and Asia. Clients include government entities, developers, energy majors and infrastructure funds.
For further details, candidates fulfilling the above criteria are invited to send their CV in complete confidence to
